import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';


const Navigation = () => ( <
    nav >
    <
    div className = "nav-links" >
    <
    ul >
    <
    li > < Link to = "/" > Articles < /Link> </li >
    <
    li > < Link to = "/about" > About < /Link> </li >
    <
    /ul>  <
    /div>  <
    /nav>
);

export default Navigation;
